{
  "page": "Lord Hewett's Town",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Lord Hewett's Town</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Folko Streese Oakenshield Port.JPG\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG/300px-Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG/450px-Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG 1.5x, /images/1/12/Folko_Streese_Oakenshield_Port.JPG 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Oakenshield\" title=\"Oakenshield\">Oakenshield</a> port by Folko Streese © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hewett\" title=\"House Hewett\">House Hewett</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Feudalism\" title=\"Feudalism\">feudal lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Religion</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Notable places</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Oakenshield_Castle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Oakenshield Castle\">Oakenshield Castle</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Lord Hewett&#39;s Town\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Lord Hewett&#39;s Town\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/400px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/800px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 40%; left: 23.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Lord Hewett&#39;s Town\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Lord Hewett&#39;s Town\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Lord Hewett's Town</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> and the location of Lord Hewett's Town\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Hewett's Town</b> is a large town on the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Oakenshield\" title=\"Oakenshield\">Oakenshield</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. It is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hewett\" title=\"House Hewett\">House Hewett</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapters_that_take_place_at_Lord_Hewett.27s_Town\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapters that take place at Lord Hewett's Town</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Twice as big as <a href=\"/index.php/Lordsport\" title=\"Lordsport\">Lordsport</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Pyke_(island)\" title=\"Pyke (island)\">Pyke</a>, Lord Hewett's Town contains a stone quay, a pier-lined harbor, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">sept</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Oakenshield_Castle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Oakenshield Castle\">Oakenshield Castle</a> sits above the town's harbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Hewett's Town is captured by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> during their <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>. Though shops and houses are looted, only the <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">sept</a> is burned.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">King of the Isles and the North</a>, uses the town as his seat of power while he remains in the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_Islands\" title=\"Shield Islands\">Shield Islands</a>. Euron decrees that widows and orphans from the battle are to be sold as <a href=\"/index.php/Slaves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slaves\">slaves</a> instead of being taken back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Thrall\" title=\"Thrall\">thralls</a>, which disturbs <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The streets were strewn with corpses, each with a small flock of <a href=\"/index.php/Crow\" title=\"Crow\">carrion crows</a> in attendance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span id=\"Chapters_that_take_place_at_Lord_Hewett's_Town\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapters_that_take_place_at_Lord_Hewett.27s_Town\">Chapters that take place at Lord Hewett's Town</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Chapters that take place at Lord Hewett&#039;s Town\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 29\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i>: 29. The Reaver</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Hewett%27s_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"gl